com.wowza.gocoder.sdk.api.logging

Class WZLog

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wowza.gocoder.sdk.api.logging.WZLog

  • public final class WZLog
extends Object
    The WZLog class provides a collection of static API methods for sending logging output.

    Usage example:

             private final static String TAG = "MyClassName";

         WZLog.LOGGING_ENABLED = true;
         WZLog.info(TAG, "Become a Wowza Ninja today!");
         try {
             ... code which throws an exception ...
         } catch (Exception e) {
             WZLog.error(TAG, "An error occurred", e);
         }
